name: space guardian Chew in love
description:
"One of the veterans of the space guardian group, he has been trought a lot in those milennia, but he is strong and willing, as long as there is danger, Chew will be there to defend the realities. It has several altered body parts with technologies from different parts of the galaxy"

this work was created in the pixelpetz game by me (@eitaivan). i produced a series of original alien characters, exploring linking science fiction, fantasy and horror references.
